title: Not getting new missions.

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: I completed the first mission a couple of weeks ago and I've not gotten any new ones. Is this a bug or have I missed something?

replies.body: Those missions were for the [versus ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/qeNowEPO-versus-event)event, which is now over.  :(  There are 2 new missions available, but they are specifically if you've unlocked Kayn.  Let me know if that clears things up!
